    <ns0:task id="activity_hospitals_prereq_combined_mod" name="implement a common standardized risk stratification assessment tool or process to determine where and how to assist with clinical decision making when patients present to the emergency department AND have a pathway or mechanism to transfer patients to a higher level provider AND develop and consistently apply risk-stratification tools that can be used for multiple conditions (including HF) (Role: Ontario hospitals)">
